x=\tan u
\int \frac{\sqrt{x^2+1}}{x}dx
\sqrt{x^2+1}=u
\int \frac{x\sqrt{x^2+1}}{x^2}\,dx.
x^2+1=u^2
2x\,dx=2u\,du
\int \frac{u^2}{u^2-1} \, du.
\cosh^2(t)-\sinh^2(t)=1
x=\sinh(t)
\int \frac{\sqrt{x^2 + 1}}{x} dx
u = \sqrt{x^2 + 1}\implies x = \pm \sqrt{u^2-1}
du = -(x^2 + 1)^{-\frac{1}{2}}2x dx \implies dx = -(\sqrt{x^2+1})\frac{1}{2x}du
dx = -\left(\sqrt{u^2 - 1+1}\right)\frac{1}{\pm2\sqrt{u^2-1}}du = \mp\frac{u}{2\sqrt{u^2-1}}du
\int \frac{u}{\pm \sqrt{u^2-1}}\left(\mp\frac{u}{2\sqrt{u^2-1}}\right)du
\int \frac{u^2}{u^2-1}du
\int 1 + \frac{1}{(u-1)(u+1)}du
\frac{1}{(u-1)(u+1)} = \frac{1}{2(u-1)} - \frac{1}{2(u+1)}
\int 1 + \frac{1}{2(u-1)} - \frac{1}{2(u+1)}du
u + \frac{1}{2}\ln(u-1) - \frac{1}{2}\ln(u+1) + C
u + \frac{1}{2}\ln\left(\frac{u-1}{u+1}\right) + C
\sqrt{x^2 + 1} + \frac{1}{2}\ln\left(\frac{\sqrt{x^2 + 1}-1}{\sqrt{x^2 + 1}+1}\right) + C
\sqrt{x^2 + 1} + \frac{1}{2}\ln\left(\frac{x^2 + 1 - 1}{\left(\sqrt{x^2 + 1}+1\right)^2}\right) + C
\sqrt{x^2 + 1} + \frac{1}{2}\ln(x^2) - \frac{1}{2}\ln\left({\left(\sqrt{x^2 + 1}+1\right)^2}\right) + C
\sqrt{x^2 + 1} + \ln(x) - \ln\left({\sqrt{x^2 + 1}+1}\right) + C
